@NODE "History" "History"
@NEXT "Thanks"

@{code}@{jcenter}@{fg shine}History@{fg text}
@{jleft}@{fg fill}Release 7:@{fg text}

 · TOTALLY overhalued the guide to support MultiView v40+ (you should find it
   faster to view now).
 · Added about 60 - 70 new buttons and cleaned up many others (@{b}NOTE@{ub}: if you
   have old buttons from a previous release of this archive, you should replace
   ALL of them with the ones in this archive).
 · Also included @{"Leo's" LINK "Author"} @{fg fill}a@{fg shine}w@{fg text}e@{fg shine}s@{fg fill}o@{fg text}m@{fg shine}e@{fg text} assembler utils @{"DOpusFuncs and CDOpus" LINK "LeoASM"}!!
   (Included in the @{"c drawer" LINK "C"} with their respective documentation).
 · Made buttons for the newly released OpusFTP module!
 · Included icons for ALL buttons!
 · Totally overhauled the @{"Buttons_Template" SYSTEM "sys:utilities/multiview button_template"} !
 · Added lots more @{"Hints&Tips" LINK "HintsTips"} and updated the Guide.
 · Added some new @{"Patterns" LINK "Patterns"}.
 · Added @{"Images2" LINK "Images2"} and @{"Images3" LINK "Images3"} drawers.
 · Included ALL @{"Leo's" LINK "Author"} @{"ARexx scripts" LINK "ARexx"} (@{b}NOTE@{ub}: All scripts are NEW and should
   replace any which you already have with the same name).
 · Removed the Drives drawer - drives icons are now in @{"Icons (dir)" LINK "Icons"} and the
   brushes are in @{"Images3 (dir)" LINK "Images3"}.
 · Included a DOpus5 survey - please take the time to fill it out!
 · Added an @{"INDEX" LINK "Index"}.
 · New @{"NudelScreen.pic" SYSTEM "sys:utilities/multiview nudelscreen.pic"}.
 · New @{"NudelScreen2.pic" SYSTEM "sys:utilities/multiview nudelscreen2.pic"} which shows off Opus' power.
 · Fixed the @{"Wizard Developments" LINK "LeoD5PM_OrderInfo"} fax number which was incorrect on the
   registration card. (Note: The number was tested and it appears to be an
   answering machine for Wizard, not a fax, unless it is auto-detect).
 · Updated @{"PolarSmall-Prop.font" LINK "Fonts"} (only a slight change).
 · Changed the @{"SYSOPS.README" SYSTEM "sys:utilities/multiview sysops.readme"} file.
 · Added a @{"Quick Introduction" LINK "QuickIntro"}.
 · Added a @{"NOT Shareware" LINK "NotShareWare"} note. (dig dig dig...).
 · Moved the DirectoryOpus & DOpus_Startup icons into the @{"icons drawer" LINK "Icons"}.

@{fg fill}@{" Release 6 " LINK "R6"}
@{fg fill}@{" Release 5 " LINK "R5"}
@{fg fill}@{" Release 4 " LINK "R4"}
@{fg fill}@{" Release 3 " LINK "R3"}
@{fg fill}@{" Release 2 " LINK "R2"}
@{fg fill}@{" Release 1 " LINK "R1"}

