@PREV "IM"

@{code}@{jcenter}@{fg shine}IconMaker by Tobias Ferber - part of the ITools archive@{fg text}
@{jleft}
@{body}IM (IconMaker) is one of many small icon utilities included in ITools_1.42.lha
written by Tobias Ferber (ferber@rpk.mach.uni-karlsruhe.de). IM converts a
specified brush into an icon. You can find the ITools archive on Aminet.

